Mark Ward Faville was found guilty of voluntary manslaughter in the death of his wife Anne , who died in 2000 after being suffocated in a homicidal manner . 
  After the verdict was read he took his own life in the courthouse in Christiansburg, Virginia . 
  He was found dead of a self-inflicted wound and it is not known how he did it . 
  Anne died of a heart attack after she choked on a piece of chicken . 
 